For this assignment, I have implemented all required functionality, mostly in the new curse_main.c file, all controls are functional, the trainer menu works and is scrollable using the ncurses pad window, and when colliding with an npc you do start a battle with them. Color is implemented, although it may not be perfect. For any of the keys such as quit (Q) or >, the shift key is required, as I was unsure if the specification meant the key (> for example) itself or the actual character. I did add another function as well that randomly generates names for the NPCs, so those will show in the trainer menu. while I did rename my files, to run it still is ./assignment01 .